v1.0.8 release

New: plpgsql FUNCTION soberano."z-fn_Helper_process_modify"(character varying, character varying[], inputqties numeric[], character varying[])
	for easing process configuration directly on database, or migration, or data entering, ...
	
New: In order.zul , enforce that "subprocess" is an illegal value for the text box 'Special instructions...'
	
Fix: Default Tomcat DB connection pool parameters changed.

Fix: Avoid showing subprocess entries in order form (FUNCTION soberano."fn_Order_get")

Fix: Avoid showing subprocess entries in order tickets (FUNCTION soberano."fn_Order_getTicket")

Fix: Avoid retrieving subprocess allocations (FUNCTION soberano."fn_Order_getProductionLineGroupedAllocations")

Fix: Avoid retrieving subprocess allocations (FUNCTION soberano."fn_ProcessRunOutputAllocation_getAll")

Fix: Avoid showing subprocess allocations in report (FUNCTION soberano."fn_ProcessRunOutputAllocation_getReport")

Fix: Avoid showing subprocess allocations in report (FUNCTION soberano."fn_ProcessRunOutputAllocation_getReportMinimal")

Fix: Delete subprocess process runs upon order reopening (FUNCTION soberano."fn_Order_reopen")
	
